| 🔴 Critical | 2 | LINQ chain + `.ToLower()` in per-string hot path — ~6 allocations per `Humanize()` call |
| 🟡 Moderate | 4 | Unused Concat helper, params array, double-Humanize, unsealed classes |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

